name: JvmSuppressWildcards
signature: @Target([AnnotationTarget.CLASS, AnnotationTarget.FUNCTION, AnnotationTarget.PROPERTY, AnnotationTarget.TYPE]) annotation class JvmSuppressWildcards

items.desc: Instructs compiler to generate or omit wildcards for type arguments corresponding to parameters with declaration-site variance, for example such as Collection<out T> has.
Returns a KClass instance corresponding to the annotation type of this annotation.
